OL,3,CBristol Airport plans include longer
OL,4,Crunway for flights to US and Middle
OL,5,CEast
OL,7,FBristol Airport has revealed its
OL,8,Fexpansion masterplan and it includes a
OL,9,Fbigger terminal, a runway extension
OL,10,Fand more shops on site.
OL,12,FThe proposals would see flights
OL,13,Fincrease from just shy of 86,000 a
OL,14,Fyear to 100,000 and include plans to
OL,15,Foffer new destinations in the Middle
OL,16,FEast and east coast of the US.
OL,18,FIf approved, the airport's passenger
OL,19,Fcapacity would go from 12 million a
OL,20,Fyear to 15 million a year by 2036.
