OL,7,FThe airport's bosses say the expansion
OL,8,Fwill "meet future demand for air
OL,9,Ftravel in the region" and say its plan
OL,10,Fincludes road and public transport
OL,11,Fimprovements as well as more parking
OL,12,Fand a new hotel.
OL,14,FAs first revealed by ITV News West
OL,15,FCountry earlier this month, Bristol
OL,16,FAirport wants to grow further and has
OL,17,Ftoday launched a consultation setting
OL,18,Fout a masterplan to 2040.
OL,20,FAmong the proposals are:
