OL,7,F"Work is also ongoing to decarbonise
OL,8,Foperations at the airport on projects
OL,9,Fremoving gas from our site, to be
OL,10,Freplaced with heat pumps."
OL,12,FThe plans are sure to meet with fierce
OL,13,Fopposition. North Somerset Council
OL,14,Frejected the airport's current
OL,15,Fexpansion when first proposed in 2020
OL,16,Fbut the airport's owners won on a High
OL,17,FCourt appeal.
